Package: splits
Type: Package
Title: SPecies' LImits by Threshold Statistics 
Version: 1.0-8
Date: 2009-01-16
Author: Thomas Ezard, Tomochika Fujisawa and Tim Barraclough
Maintainer: Thomas Ezard <thomas.ezard@imperial.ac.uk>
Description: "splits" contains tools for delimiting species and automated taxonomy at multiple levels of biological organization (eg. DNA barcoding, morphometrics), both top-down (merging phylogenetic and phylogeographic methods) and bottom-up (single samples into >1 groups).
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 2.6.0), ape, MASS, paran
LazyLoad: yes
